<div class="modal-header">
  <div class="btn-group pull-right">
    <button class="btn btn-success sync-sapir-data ">
      Close and login as Ed Sapir
    </button>
    <a class="btn btn-success dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#"> 
      <i class="icon-user icon-white"></i> 
      Login 
      <span class="caret"></span> 
    </a>
    <ul class="dropdown-menu">
      <li class="not-a">
        Username:
        <input id="welcomeusername" size="16" type="text">
      </li>
      <li class="not-a">
        Password:
        <input id="welcomepassword" size="16" type="password">
      </li>
      <li class="not-a">
        <button class="btn btn-success sync-my-data" >
          Sync my data to this computer
        </button>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h1> Welcome to iField! <small>beta</small></h1>
    <i> iField: An offline/online fieldlinguistics database which
    adapts to its user's I-Language.</i>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
  <p>
    Welcome Beta Testers! Please sit back with a cup of tea and watch this play list before you begin testing iField. Leave us notes, bugs, comments, suggestions etc in the Contact Us/Bug Report form at the bottom of the page. We will try to address all your comments before August 1st. </p>
    <p>Have fun and happy bug hunting!
  </p>
  <iframe width="500" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PL984DA79F4B314FAA&amp;hl=en_US" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  <div class=" alert alert-error hide "></div>
  <div class="well create_new_user_password">
    <h3>Or create a new user</h3>
    <p>
      http://ifield.fieldlinguist.com/{{username}}
    </p>
    <label> What is your username going to be? </label>
    <span class="like-form-inline">
      <input class="username" value="{{username}}" type="text"/>
      <button class="btn btn-primary new-user-button" value="">New User</button>
    </span>
    <div class="hide confirm-password">
      <label>Password</label>
      <input class="password" type="password">
      </input>
      <label>Confirm Password</label>
      <input class="to-confirm-password"
      type="password">
      </input>
      <br />
      <button class="btn btn-success register-new-user">
        Sign in
        with password
      </button>
      <!-- Hiding Twitter and facebook because I dont think anyone will use them now. <button class="btn btn-success register-twitter">
        <i class="i icon-twitter"></i> Sign in with Twitter
      </button>
      <button class="btn btn-success register-facebook">
        <i class="i icon-facebook"></i> Sign in with Facebook
      </button> -->
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="alert alert-block"><!-- moved here so that it can be seen on smaller screens by scrolling -->
    <a class="close" data-dismiss="alert" href="#">Ã—</a>
    <h4 class="alert-heading">Warning!</h4>
    This is an beta version of iField, it might smile and make bubbles
    but it also burps, vomits and sleeps at inopportune times... 
  </div>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
</div>